fullText: Step into the latest bariatric care approaches in this live webinar on Zoom — covering everything from pre-op planning to long-term post-op nutrition management. 🔍 Essential techniques you’ll explore: ✔️ Prepare patients nutritionally before surgery & implement liver-shrinking diets ✔️ Manage post-op meal progression & hydration effectively ✔️ Monitor micronutrients and provide evidence-based supplementation ✔️ Address complications like dumping syndrome, hypoglycemia, and weight regain ✔️ Use counseling techniques to improve adherence & support lasting success ✔️ Apply real case examples with practical nutrition monitoring tools 💥 Early Bird Pricing Now Available: Message us “Bariatric” through the WhatsApp link in bio to claim your early bird #LiveWebinar #BariatricNutrition #ClinicalNutrition #DietitianCourse #CME #NutritionStrategies #CatalystCourses #ESPEN #ASMBS
